  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast is an extensive hot and cold buffet</p>
<p>A full buffet dinner is served twice a week and a semi-served dinner is served five times a week</p>
<p>On a Thursday and Saturday guests can replace their regular dinner with a fondue for a supplement (€15pp for cheese and €20pp for meat and shrimp gourmet fondue)</p>]]></cateringDescription>
