  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>The Valamar Obertauern Hotel is the perfect place to hit the slopes and unwind. The hotel offers a family friendly experience, extensive spa area, and </span>ski in, ski out location.</p>
<h2>Ski in, ski out</h2>
<p><span>The hotel is just a three minute walk from the centre of Obertauern and has a perfect location right on the slopes, so you can ski in and ski out hassle-free.</span></p>
<h2>Indoor, outdoor pool</h2>
<p>New for this season, the Valamar <span>Obertauern </span>Hotel has extended its already impressive wellness facilities to add a 88<span>m² indoor, outdoor pool. You can enjoy the fresh mountain air from the heated pool or explore the rest of the 770m² Balance spa. The spa has everything you'll need including a steam bath, infrared sauna, </span>tranquillity room, snow grotto, and Finnish and bio saunas.</p>
<h2>Family friendly</h2>
<p>There is something to entertain all the family including a soft play room, fun zone with video games, and cinema corner showing cartoons and family films. The Maro kids' club runs an excellent supervised entertainment programme for 3-12 year olds.</p>
<h2>Sustainability</h2>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;">The hotel supports local craftsmen and uses environmentally sustainable materials and processes in the design of its rooms and exterior. They encourage the use of locally sourced ingredients in their dishes.</span></p>
<div class="MjjYud"><span id="z9PoV"></span></div>
<p>Please note images of the hotel pool are artist's impressions.</p>]]></description>
